data.title: St. Joseph Catholic Church
data.text:
Mentions "ex missione Westphalia" for groom. Possibly meaning he just returned from Westphalia.

Ode is a variant spelling of Ott per relative jkramer

Date is out of sequence. Maybe 25 Jun?

Marriage not sanctified due to Lutheran witnesses?

Entered twice - 4 Feb and 6 Feb 1844.

This date is confusing as it comes before May 1842. 7bris =Sep

From (to) Waterloo, IL; From (to) Iowa.

Bride is from Louisville; also mentions Chicago.
